Subject: Introduction to Exoplanet Art with the GIMP 1
Description:
Missions like the Kepler telescope have shown our galaxy be home to countless exoplanets, but it is still up to artists to imagine how these planets.  Discover how easy it is for someone with no artistic experience to create beautiful exoplanet images with the open source editor the GIMP.
                                       Speakers include:Jason Rutherford - Track: Science  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none

Subject: Kalidasia Fleet Commander - The Siege of Cadre 4
Description: The Surakari have invaded Cadre 4 and it is up to a small Heragul fleet to hold the aliens at bay. Come defend Cadre 4(or destroy it!) in this two player asymmetrical game of planetary siege.  Speakers include:Jason Rutherford - Track: Gaming  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
